      "author": "Alvin Mustafa",
      "authorUrl": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100589613549490472301?hl=id",
      "rating": 5,
      "text": "Ordered Nasi Gule Sapi, Bakwan and 1 drink for around 60k. The spacious place with simple yet tasty food. The ambience was so calm and refreshing (if you are the only one visitor there). I assume this place could be also rented for private outdoor event.",
